Slice chicken breasts into 32 pieces. Spray a large skillet with olive oil flavored cooking spray. Saute chicken, onion, and green pepper for 6 to 8 minutes. Stir in drained tomatoes and tomato sauce. Add SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener, Italian seasoning, olives, and black pepper. Mix well to combine. Lower heat and simmer for 10-15 minutes, stirring occasionally. For each serving, place 1/2 cup pasta on a plate and spoon 2/3 cup sauce over top.